I think this magical weapon

13
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,500
doesn't seem to be useful.

14
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,450
It's not even as good as
my bamboo ladle.

15
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,940
If you're going to call me stupid,

16
00:02:00,190 --> 00:02:01,100
don't say it.

17
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,290
What about

18
00:02:10,920 --> 00:02:12,190
lending me your demon staff?

19
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:13,030
No way.

20
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:16,380
Why are you so stingy?

21
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,530
Isn't that
what the Water Demon King said?

22
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,690
This is a low-level magical weapon.

23
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:23,410
Besides, it looks quite old.

24
00:02:23,830 --> 00:02:25,530
Why do you value it so much?

25
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,500
My sister gave it to me.

26
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:35,410
When I was little,

27
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,410
I didn't have any magical weapons.

28
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,460
My sister made this demon staff for me.

29
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:45,340
This is my most precious possession.

30
00:02:56,670 --> 00:02:57,510
Mu Sheng,

31
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,410
have you noticed that

32
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:01,190
everything about Sister Mu

33
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:02,530
is extremely important to you?

34
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:05,220
But you never
took your feelings into account.

35
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,780
I was never important.

36
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:12,810
How can you think like that?

37
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:14,120
Everyone's existence

38
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,500
has its meaning.

39
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,850
The reason I live in this world

40
00:03:21,270 --> 00:03:22,530
is to protect,

41
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,080
assist,

42
00:03:24,990 --> 00:03:26,160
and fulfill my sister.

43
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,500
Apart from that,

44
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,500
I don't know why

45
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,480
a monster like me

46
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,730
should live.

47
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:43,780
You are not a monster.

48
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:45,810
And

49
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:50,000
I think you need

50
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,730
to see a psychologist.

51
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,360
See what?

52
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,340
The stars.

53
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:02,880
Look.

54
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:04,510
Come.

55
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:11,510
Mu Sheng,

56
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:13,810
do you remember

57
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:16,970
the world I told my dad

58
00:04:17,350 --> 00:04:18,610
in Taicang County?

59
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:22,310
Yes, I remember.

60
00:04:23,590 --> 00:04:24,790
It's a strange world

61
00:04:24,790 --> 00:04:26,260
without demons and magic skills.

62
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,820
In that world,

63
00:04:32,350 --> 00:04:34,460
I was an ordinary girl

64
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,700
with an ordinary appearance,

65
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,050
personality

66
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,700
and job.

67
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,700
My life is ordinary, too.

68
00:04:43,150 --> 00:04:44,530
But

69
00:04:46,710 --> 00:04:48,340
I still want to go back.

70
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,050
Because that is

71
00:04:54,910 --> 00:04:56,700
my real world.

72
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,430
Everything I have experienced here,

73
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:02,580
is an unrealistic existence

74
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,100
for me.

75
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,050
I know

76
00:05:15,910 --> 00:05:17,970
you think I'm talking nonsense.

77
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,780
I'm listening.

78
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,580
At first

79
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:32,370
I looked forward to going home every day.

80
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,460
I can't wait,

81
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,530
not even for a moment.

82
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,370
But today

83
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,520
I suddenly

84
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:47,050
realized that

85
00:05:53,230 --> 00:05:54,780
I'm beginning to feel reluctant to leave.

86
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,410
I know

87
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,340
that when the dream ends,

88
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:08,460
I will never see Sister Mu Yao,

89
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:11,290
Brother Liu

90
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:15,970
and you again.

91
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:23,410
Because of all of you,

92
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:28,170
I have begun to feel a sense of belonging
to this world,

93
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,700
to believe in everything here

94
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,730
and to integrate into it.

95
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:39,900
I believe there are demons,

96
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:42,660
magic skills,

97
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:45,730
and spiritual powers here.

98
00:06:49,230 --> 00:06:50,530
I believe

99
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,780
it all really exists.

100
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:00,960
You

101
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,050
didn't believe that before?

102
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,360
I used to think

103
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,370
it was absurd,

104
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,220
like a fairy tale.

105
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,530
When practicing magic skills,

106
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,850
I didn't have a sense of conviction.

107
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,800
So when I taught you
the Four Phases Technique,

108
00:07:33,850 --> 00:07:35,700
and when I taught you
to hold your breath and concentrate,

109
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:37,290
you didn't believe it.

110
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,290
No wonder you couldn't master it.

111
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:44,970
Is that the main point?

112
00:07:48,590 --> 00:07:49,610
Come down, Lin Yu.

113
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,530
My disciple

114
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,220
must not embarrass me.

115
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,520
Wait.

116
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,160
What?

117
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:02,020
I can continue practicing

118
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:03,370
if you agree

119
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,260
to one condition of mine.

120
00:08:05,590 --> 00:08:06,430
What condition?

121
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,750
From now on,

122
00:08:12,150 --> 00:08:13,580
don't call me Lin Yu,

123
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:14,900
call me Miaomiao,

124
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:16,070
okay?

125
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,480
Why?

126
00:08:17,590 --> 00:08:18,430
Because

127
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,150
I told you before,

128
00:08:22,150 --> 00:08:23,530
my nickname is Miaomiao.

129
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:24,720
From now on,

130
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,410
I'll call you Ziqi.

131
00:08:27,030 --> 00:08:28,050
You call me Miaomiao.

132
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,820
As you wish.

133
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:41,180
Then call me.

134
00:08:47,350 --> 00:08:48,460
Just call me.

135
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,920
Miaomiao.

136
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:00,920
Ziqi.

137
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:15,300
♪The sky in my eyes is always dazzling blue♪

138
00:09:16,700 --> 00:09:17,750
Come and practice magic skills.

139
