that was destroyed years ago?

716
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:15,170
Why do you speak so harshly?

717
00:38:17,150 --> 00:38:18,070
Why is your face like that?

718
00:38:18,070 --> 00:38:18,940
I'm asking you a question.

719
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:22,290
You said that the Mitu Valley brings
misfortune and disaster, did you?

720
00:38:23,240 --> 00:38:24,610
I didn't say that.

721
00:38:25,110 --> 00:38:27,150
That's what happened.

722
00:38:27,150 --> 00:38:28,440
If you don't believe me,

723
00:38:28,440 --> 00:38:30,400
you can go to the town

724
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,590
and ask around.

725
00:38:31,590 --> 00:38:33,510
As long as a person enters

726
00:38:33,510 --> 00:38:34,580
the Mitu Valley,

727
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,900
he won't come to a good end.

728
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:43,500
You're not thinking
of entering the valley,

729
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:45,020
are you?

730
00:38:45,720 --> 00:38:47,100
Don't worry about it.

731
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:48,720
That place is

732
00:38:48,720 --> 00:38:49,840
very dangerous.

733
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:51,210
You shouldn't go there.

734
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:52,640
Let's go.

735
00:38:53,070 --> 00:38:54,630
For the sake of fellow practitioners,

736
00:38:54,630 --> 00:38:56,110
I'm trying to persuade you.

737
00:38:56,110 --> 00:38:57,590
You shouldn't be so self-righteous.

738
00:38:57,590 --> 00:38:59,110
Young Master Fuyi, whatever happens,

739
00:38:59,110 --> 00:38:59,950
don't…

740
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:04,940
Boast and mystify things.

741
00:39:06,110 --> 00:39:07,630
I think

742
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:10,060
this valley must have
an unspeakable secret.

743
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:11,460
So you think

744
00:39:11,590 --> 00:39:12,750
he deliberately started the rumor

745
00:39:12,750 --> 00:39:14,020
to stop people from entering the valley?

746
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,460
It's possible.

747
00:39:16,990 --> 00:39:17,800
Let's sleep for the night

748
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,840
and enter the valley tomorrow.

749
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:19,960
If he is hiding something,

750
00:39:19,960 --> 00:39:21,210
we'll find out tomorrow.

